I'm Chief Scientific Advisor to Match.com,

00:03:31.347 --> 00:03:33.027
I've been it for 11 years.

00:03:33.051 --> 00:03:35.055
I keep telling them
and they agree with me,

00:03:35.079 --> 00:03:36.618
that these are not dating sites,

00:03:36.642 --> 00:03:38.655
they are introducing sites.

00:03:39.017 --> 00:03:41.280
When you sit down in a bar,

00:03:41.304 --> 00:03:42.888
in a coffee house,

00:03:42.912 --> 00:03:44.268
on a park bench,

00:03:44.292 --> 00:03:49.297
your ancient brain snaps into action
like a sleeping cat awakened,

00:03:49.321 --> 00:03:50.620
and you smile

00:03:50.644 --> 00:03:51.802
and laugh

00:03:51.826 --> 00:03:53.008
and listen

00:03:53.032 --> 00:03:57.905
and parade the way our ancestors
did 100,000 years ago.

